title: SouthernCharm: Hatin' On Peyton
description:
Naomie is on a rampage these days, and no one on "Southern Charm" is safe, especially not the newbie Peyton. It's another takedown... but was it warranted? We get into all that plus talk "Southern Charm New Orleans" and Crappens Mailbag to finish out the week. Come listen!

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.
